  "texts": [
    "The bits in molecular fingerprints corresponded to different chemical groups, and the fingerprint with a high Gini coefficient indicated the hepatotoxic risk of the chemicals in the study [13].",
    "A few attempts have also been made to develop deep-learning models based on molecular fingerprints [15,16].",
    "A convolutional neural network (CNN) based on embedded molecular fingerprint features was used for predicting DILI [16].",
    "However, most of the studies focused on performance improvement rather than interpretation.",
    "In addition, nearly all the studies identified feature importance only for feature selection or specific models."
